item.title: Subclassing with PyCharm
item.description: Today has been a day filled with writing and rewriting code. For the last few days I have bashing around in a command line UI system called Textual. It is a Python based Rapid Application Development framework that lets you build TUI applications. Terminal User Interface. If it isn’t the geekiest thing I have ever done I don’t know what is.
